20the%20couch%20he%20was%20touching%20my%20legs%20and%20said%2C%20Put%20on%20spa%20music%20and%20I%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2024%2F01%2F17%2Fnew-airbnb-host-raped-first-guest-court-told%2F%5C%22%3Egive%20you%20a%20massage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20police%20-%20according%20to%20The%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20alleged%20that%20Dellarovere%20then%20sexually%20assaulted%20and%20raped%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfterwards%2C%20she%20went%20into%20her%20own%20bedroom%20and%20barricaded%20herself%20in%20her%20room%20with%20her%20kitchen%20knive%2C%20her%20dog%20and%20cat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20he%20returned%20at%20about%202%20am%20and%20went%20to%20sleep%20in%20the%20spare%20room.%20The%20following%20morning%2C%20before%20leaving%2C%20he%20allegedly%20told%20her%3A%20%26quot%3BI'll%20leave%20a%20good%20review%2C%26quot%3B%20reported%20the%20Telegraph.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20told%20police%20she%20initially%20thought%20about%20just%20reporting%20the%20matter%20to%20Airbnb%20but%20then%20decided%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%2C%20reported%20The%20Telegraph.%20%26quot%3BThen%20my%20thought%20was%20that%20he%20is%20likely%20going%20to%20do%20that%20to%20someone%20again%20so%20I%20want%20his%20name%20to%20be%20flagged%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%2C%20however%2C%20has%20denied%20raping%20the%20woman%20or%20sexually%20assaulting%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705628160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fgs7duut8_londoin_625x300_19_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flondon-airbnb-host-alleges-rape-by-her-1st-guest-report-4890113%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20in%20London%20has%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20raped%20by%20her%20first%20guest%20at%20her%20home%20that%20she%20had%20rented%20out%20through%20Airbnb.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement