%5C%22%3Emidrange%20line%20of%20Swift%20laptops%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20the%20Ultra%20series%2C%20portability%20comes%20before%20power%20%E2%80%94%20although%20the%20best%20models%20will%20offer%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%2014th-generation%20HX-series%20laptop%20CPUs%2C%20the%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20processors%20are%20geared%20at%20a%20much%20wider%20audience.%20If%20you%20plan%20on%20buying%20a%20midrange%20laptop%20or%20notebook%20PC%20this%20year%20with%20an%20Intel%20chip%2C%20it'll%20probably%20have%20a%20Core%20Ultra.%20Truly%20budget%20devices%20will%20likely%20stick%20with%2012th%20or%2013th-generation%20CPUs.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20laptop%20models%20available%20now%20with%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20a%20new%20Intel%20computer%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20a%20computer%20with%20a%20new%20Intel%20Core%20CPU%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222161%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20logos%20for%20the%20Intel%20Core%20i5%2C%20i7%2C%20and%20i9%20against%20a%20white%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a01686dcdb354a9856be7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221620%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEvery%20CPU%20generation%20comes%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20different%20models.%3Cp%3EIntel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20mainline%2014th-generation%20CPUs%2C%20it%20really%20depends%20on%20the%20price.%20Intel%20has%20set%20its%20MSRP%20at%20the%20same%20price%20as%20the%20older%2013th%20generation%2C%20so%20ideally%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20be%20paying%20that%20much%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20large%20majority%20of%20consumers%2C%20the%20Intel%20Core%2014th%20generation's%20improvements%20are%20marginal%2C%20and%20not%20worth%20spending%20a%20huge%20chunk%20of%20money%20for.%20Only%20professional%20or%20enterprise%20users%20doing%20intense%20work%20in%20bulk%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20editors%20rendering%20multiple%204K%20videos%20each%20day%2C%20or%20finance%20workers%20jumping%20between%20dozens%20of%20massive%20spreadsheets%20%E2%80%94%20will%20appreciate%20the%20small%20performance%20gains.%20But%20many%20of%20those%20same%20enterprise%20users%20would%20probably%20be%20better%20off%20buying%20an%20enterprise-focused%20CPU%20like%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amd.com%2Fen%2Fprocessors%2Fryzen-threadripper-pro%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAMD%20Threadripper%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can't%20afford%20a%20PC%20with%20an%20Intel%2014th-generation%20CPU%2C%20don't%20panic.%20The%20cheaper%2013th-generation%20CPUs%20are%20still%20fantastic%2C%20and%20AMD's%20current%20top-tier%20Ryzen%20processors%20are%20great%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%2C%20most%20consumers%20aren't%20going%20to%20have%20much%20choice%20over%20whether%20they%20buy%20a%20new%20laptop%20with%20one%20or%20not.%20After%20all%2C%20you%20can't%20build%20your%20own%20laptop%20(not%20easily%2C%20at%20least)%2C%20and%20most%20laptop%20companies%20don't%20offer%20many%20customization%20options.%20Companies%20like%20Asus%20are%20actively%20porting%20the%20majority%20of%20their%20Intel-based%20laptops%20over%20to%20the%20Ultra%20lineup%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20a%20bad%20thing.%20Core%20Ultra%20chips%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20higher%20end%2C%20are%20great%20processors%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20users.%20They%20don't%20offer%20much%20of%20a%20performance%20boost%20over%20similarly%20priced%20hardware%2C%20but%20their%20better%20power%20efficiency%20means%20longer%20battery%20life%20and%20lower%20temperatures.%20Besides%2C%20if%20you're%20using%20a%20thin%20laptop%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20expect%20maximum%20performance%20anyway.%20And%20AI%20enthusiasts%20will%20appreciate%20the%20new%20Neural%20Processing%20Unit.