y%20be%20the%20CPU%20of%20choice%20for%20casual%20AI%20hobbyists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInformation%20about%20Arrow%20and%20Lunar%20Lake%20is%20scarce%2C%20so%20only%20time%20will%20tell%20whether%20they%20end%20up%20replacing%20Raptor%20and%20Meteor%20Lake%20or%20simply%20complementing%20them.%20Either%20way%2C%202024%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20big%20year%20for%20Intel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fintel-14th-generation-core-and-core-ultra-release-date-specs%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705622328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a017486979d73718227a59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fintel-14th-generation-core-and-core-ultra-release-date-specs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Intel's%20new%2014th-generation%20Core%20and%20Core%20Ultra%20(%26quot%3BMeteor%20Lake%26quot%3B)%20CPUs%20are%20now%20available.%20Here's%20a%20rundown%20of%20details%20and%20computers%20you%20can%20buy%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wantonelli%40insider.com%20(William%20Antonelli)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fintel-14th-generation-core-and-core-ultra-release-date-specs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%2012-3-30%20'hot%20girl%20workout'%20is%20a%20waste%20of%20your%20time%20%E2%80%94%20these%203%20routines%20are%20better%20for%20building%20muscle%20and%20burning%20fat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20sports%20bra%20and%20shorts%20looking%20tired%20on%20a%20treadmill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a9832443bb77284b9e3db4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20break%20up%20with%20your%20treadmill%20if%20you%20get%20bored.%20Exercises%20like%20rucking%2C%20rowing%2C%20and%20lifting%20weights%20can%20be%20more%20fun%20and%20beneficial.%3Cp%3Eskynesher%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20viral%2012-3-30%20workout%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20there%20are%20better%20ways%20to%20spend%20your%20exercise%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERowing%20and%20rucking%20are%20easy%20ways%20to%20combine%20cardio%20with%20resistance%20training%20to%20build%20muscle.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%A0Don't%20shy%20away%20from%20strength%20training%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20less%20intimidating%20and%20healthier%20than%20you%20may%20think.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStep%20away%20from%20the%20treadmill%20%E2%80%94%20seriously%2C%20the%20latest%20TikTok%20trend%20is%20not%20going%20to%20give%20you%20abs%2C%20grow%20your%20butt%2C%20or%20help%20you%20get%20the%20toned%20bod%20of%20your%20dreams%20no%20matter%20what%20influencers%20say%20or%20show%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3B12-3-30%26quot%3B%20workout%2C%20otherwise%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bhot%20girl%20workout%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20zombie%20exercise%20trend%20that's%20trying%20to%20suck%20the%20life%20out%20of%20your%20gym%20sessions.%20The%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bviral%26quot%3B%20routine%20seems%20to%20be%20resurrected%20every%20few%20months%20on%20various%20social%20media%20platforms%20since%20around%202019.%20The%20gist%20of%20it%20is%20that%20you%20spend%2030%20minutes%20on%20a%20treadmill%20set%20to%20three%20miles%20per%20hour%20at%20a%2012%25%20incline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20you%20need%20to%20know%20right%20now%20is%20that%20the%2012-3-30%20trend%20is%20yet%20another%20version%20of%20the%20endless%20cardio%20machine%20trends%20with%20misleading%20promises%2C%20all%20banking%20on%20the%20myth%20that%20exercise%20is%20a%20chore%20you%20need%20to%20do%20to%20lose%20weight%20or%20look%20good.%20These%20types%20of%20workouts%20tend%20to%20target%20women%2C%20often%20playing%20on%20p