ompany%2C%20responsible%20for%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeforestation-photos-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeforestation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Amazon%20rainforest%2C%20to%20do%20even%20more%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20surrounding%20JBS's%20bid%20highlights%20the%20connection%20between%20finance%20and%20various%20drivers%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeforestation-photos-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20deforestation.%20It%20also%20raises%20questions%20about%20gauging%20claims%20that%20a%20company%20is%20committed%20to%20improving%20its%20environmental%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20companies%20listed%20on%20the%20New%20York%20and%20other%20stock%20exchanges%20have%20had%2C%20or%20still%20have%2C%20questionable%20environmental%20records.%20But%20often%20they%20have%20been%20listed%20for%20decades%2C%20having%20gone%20public%20when%20there%20was%20much%20less%20scrutiny%20of%20ecological%20impacts%20from%20business%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDozens%20of%20journalistic%20and%20NGO%20reports%20have%20shown%20that%20JBS%20is%20linked%20to%20more%20destruction%20of%20forests%20and%20other%20ecosystems%20than%20any%20other%20company%20in%20Brazil%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.booker.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2FJBS%2520SEC%2520Letter.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%20from%2015%20U.S%3C%2Fa%3E.%20senators%2C%20released%20last%20week.%20%26quot%3BThe%20company%20has%20made%20repeated%20claims%20that%20it%20will%20eliminate%20deforestation%20but%20has%20not%20taken%20meaningful%20steps%20to%20do%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20signed%20by%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans%2C%20comes%20days%20after%20a%20similar%20one%20from%2011%20British%20lawmakers%20that%20said%20letting%20JBS%20raise%20capital%20from%20shareholders%20%26quot%3Bcontradicts%20global%20efforts%20of%20governments%20and%20businesses%20to%20take%20action%20to%20mitigate%20climate%20change%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20%26quot%3Bpreserve%20essential%20natural%20habitats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20SEC%2C%20which%20has%20regulatory%20oversight%20of%20the%20NYSE%2C%20said%20it%20doesn't%20comment%20on%20individual%20filings.%20JBS%2C%20which%20applied%20in%20July%2C%20and%20the%20NYSE%20didn't%20respond%20to%20questions.%20The%20SEC%20has%20broad%20authority%20in%20regulating%20capital%20markets%2C%20including%20approving%20or%20denying%20company%20applications%20to%20get%20on%20an%20exchange%2C%20requiring%20disclosures%20and%20fining%20companies%20if%20they%20break%20financial%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo-thirds%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeat-consumption-linked-to-the-amazon-fires-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20deforestation%3C%2Fa%3E%20results%20from%20conversion%20to%20pasture%20for%20livestock%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Brazilian%20government.%20JBS%2C%20with%20the%20largest%20slaughter%20capacity%20in%20the%20region%2C%20buys%20thousands%20of%20cows%20raised%20illegally%20annually%2C%20according%20to%20audits%20by%20federal%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJBS%20has%20pledged%20to%20make%20all%20cattle%20purchases%20traceable%20by%202025%20and%20to%20reach%20net%20zero%2C%20or%20equalize%20all%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20by%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20it%20created%20the%20JBS%20Fund%20For%20the%20Amazon.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20finance%20%26quot%3Binnovative%2C%20long-term%20initiatives%20that%20build%20on%20JBS%20S.A.'s%20legacy%20of%20conservation%20and%20sustainable%20development%20in%20the%20Amazon%20Biome%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1450123%2F000121390023041583%2Fff42023_jbssa.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESEC%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E.%