0was%20swept%20away%20by%20wedding%20planning%20following%20her%20October%20engagement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20she%20and%20fianc%C3%A9%20Trevor%20Scanlon%20got%20%2420%2C000%20to%20%2430%2C000%20catering%20quotes%2C%20they%20pivoted.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EVatuone%20said%20it%20was%20empowering%20to%20reimagine%20the%20event%20%E2%80%94%20though%20there%20was%20a%20grieving%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20influencer%20and%20personal%20branding%20consultant%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annavatuone.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAnna%20Vatuone%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20who%20went%20viral%20this%20week%20for%20canceling%20her%20wedding.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20at%20age%2026%2C%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40annavatuone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egaining%20traction%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20documenting%20a%20solo%20road%20trip%20across%20the%20country%20from%20Oakland%2C%20California%2C%20to%20Boston.%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Boston%20and%20decided%20to%20stay%20on%20a%20whim.%20A%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago%2C%20I%20met%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%2C%20Trevor%2C%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20engaged%20in%20October%2C%20and%20started%20wedding%20planning%20right%20away.%20It's%20funny%20because%20I%20initially%20thought%20we%20were%20going%20to%20do%20something%20really%20small.%20That%20was%20always%20the%20vision%20I%20had%20for%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20I%20didn't%20want%20a%20big%20wedding%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20suppose%20it's%20just%20easy%20to%20get%20swept%20up%20in%20the%20process.%20You%20start%20looking%20on%20Pinterest%2C%20hearing%20other%20people's%20testimonials%20on%20TikTok%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20planning%20a%20120-person%20wedding.%20I%20wanted%20us%20both%20to%20have%20all%20the%20people%20we%20wanted%20there%2C%20so%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20keep%20extending%20the%20invitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20booked%20this%20incredible%20venue%20right%20on%20the%20water%20on%20the%20South%20Shore%20of%20Massachusetts%20for%20%246%2C000%2C%20which%20couldn't%20be%20more%20quintessential%20New%20England.%20But%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20put%20the%20deposit%20down%2C%20we%20had%20to%20get%20quotes%20from%20caterers.%20That%20was%20when%20we%20had%20to%20evaluate%20whether%20this%20was%20something%20we%20could%20really%20move%20forward%20with%20in%20good%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20quotes%20was%20%2430%2C000%3B%20another%20one%20was%20%2427%2C000.%20It%20felt%20like%20the%20minimum%20we%20could%20do%20it%20for%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20would%20be%20compromising%20on%20a%20lot%20%E2%80%94%20was%20%2422%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222743%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anna%2C%20wearing%20a%20flowy%20white%20dress%2C%20embraces%20Trevor%20on%20the%20shoreline%20in%20New%20England.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a99b6f6979d73718248142%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222058%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anna%20Vatuone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2030%2C%20the%20older%20I%20get%2C%20the%20more%20mindful%20I've%20become%20about%20money.%20And%20I%20want%20to%20make%20good%20choices%20because%20it's%20not%20only%20about%20me%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20me%20and%20Trevor%20and%20the%20future%20family%20we%20want%20to%20create.%20We%20want%20to%20have%20kids%20someday%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20are%20prepared%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EScrapping%20the%20plans%20was%20ultimately%20empowering%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20grieving%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20cancel%20our%20original%20w