%20playbook%20could%20be%20used%20against%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20might%20owe%20Sen.%20Ted%20Cruz%20an%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20no%2C%20it's%20not%20about%20the%20long%20list%20of%20things%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-ted-cruz-shouldnt-even-exist-endorsement-desantis-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Cruz%20and%20his%20family.%20Rather%2C%20it's%20about%20how%20Cruz%20and%20his%20allies%20complained%20in%202016%20about%20how%20non-Republican%20voters%20helped%20hand%20the%20nomination%20to%20Trump.%20They%20even%20tried%20to%20formally%20change%20the%20party's%20rules%20to%20incentivize%20states%20to%20move%20away%20from%20elections%20that%20allowed%20independent%20and%20possibly%20even%20Democratic%20voters%20to%20weigh%20in%20on%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20ran%20away%20with%20the%202016%20Republican%20presidential%20nomination%20in%20part%20due%20to%20his%20sheer%20dominance%20in%20these%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bopen%20primaries.%26quot%3B%20While%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Cruz%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fted-cruz-2016-most-fun-in-my-life-running-again-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggled%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20keep%20up%20by%20winning%20in%20closed%20primaries%20and%20caucuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Trump%20is%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20at%20the%20possibility%20that%20former%20UN%20Ambassador%20Nikki%20Haley%20could%20use%20his%20old%20playbook%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20know%2C%20Nikki%20Haley%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20counting%20on%20the%20Democrats%20and%20liberals%20to%20infiltrate%20your%20Republican%20primary%2C%20you%20know%20that%2C%20that's%20what's%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20New%20Hampshire%20on%20Tuesday%20evening.%20%26quot%3BA%20group%20of%20people%20coming%20in%20that%20are%20not%20Republicans%20and%20it's%20artificially%20boosting%20her%20numbers%20here%2C%20although%20we%20are%20still%20leading%20her%20by%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20illegal%20about%20Haley's%20strategy.%20New%20Hampshire%20law%20has%20long%20allowed%20unaffiliated%20voters%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20presidential%20primary.%20At%20issue%20is%20a%20long-running%20discussion%20that%20far%20pre-dates%20Trump%20about%20who%20should%20pick%20either%20of%20the%20major%20party's%20presidential%20nominees.%20Long%20ago%2C%20party%20bosses%20held%20sway%20but%20the%20progressive%20era%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitical-conventions-change%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20saw%20a%20push%20for%20broader%20primary%20elections%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20Republicans%20detest%20more%20open%20primaries%2C%20such%20rules%20challenge%20candidates%20to%20start%20building%20the%20broader%20coalition%20they%20would%20need%20to%20win%20the%20White%20House%20in%20a%20general%20election.%20It's%20a%20fact%20Haley's%20campaign%20is%20quick%20to%20bring%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNikki%20has%20always%20believed%20that%20the%20Republican%20Party%20has%20to%20be%20about%20addition%2C%20not%20subtraction.%20Republicans%20have%20lost%20the%20popular%20vote%20in%20the%20last%20seven%20of%20the%20eight%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20spokesperson%20AnnMarie%20Graham-Barnes%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20races%20we%20should%20have%20won%20in%202018%2C%202020%2C%20and%202022.%20If%20Republicans%20want%20to%20start%20winning%20again%2C%20we%20have%20to%20start%20bringing%20in%20people%20fed%20up%20with%20Joe%20Biden's%20disastrous%20administration%2C%20not%20pushing%20people%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20states%20operate%20at%20least%20a%20somewhat%20open%20primary.%20According%20to%20the%20National%20Conference%20of%20State%20Legislatures%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncsl.org%2Felections-and-campaigns%2Fstate-primary-election-types%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20eight%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20completely%20closed%20presidential%20primaries%20%E2%80%94%20most%20notably%20the%20delegate-rich%20state%20of%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20once%20ran%20up%20the%20score%20in%20open%20primaries.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20advantage%20in%20open%20primaries%20in%202016%20was%20unmistakable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2016%2F03%2F22%2Ftrumps-big-advantage-open-primaries.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20CNBC%20tally%20from%20March%202016%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20the%20future%20president%20won%20a%20greater%20percentage%20of%20primaries%20and%20caucuses%20in%20states%20with%20open%20contests.%20There's%20not%20a%20perfect%20explanation%20as%20to%20why%20though.%20Entrance%20and%20exit%20polling%20at%20the%20same%20didn't%20show%20independents%20giving%20Trump%20a%20major%20advantage%20%E2%80%94%20such%20surveys%20can%20be%20unreliable%20though.%20The%20split-screen%20between%20the%20two%20types%20of%20contests%20began%20almost%20immediately.%20Despite%20holding%20a%20polling%20advantage%20in%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%202016%20Iowa%20caucuses%2C%20Trump%20narrowly%20lost%20the%20state%20to%20Cruz.%20Iowa%2C%20unlike%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20is%20only%20partially%20open%20since%20the%20state%20requires%20voters%20to%20register%20with%20a%20party%20to%20caucus.%20Voters%20can%20change%20their%20affiliation%20on%20caucus%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20rout%20also%20stuck%20with%20Cruz's%20allies.%20Pro-Cruz%20delegates%20came%20to%20the%202016%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fstory%2F2016%2F05%2Frepublican-primary-rules-donald-trump-223136%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetermined%20to%20change%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20party's%20rules%20by%20incentivizing%20states%20to%20move%20away%20from%20open%20primaries%20or%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20practice%20altogether.%20Their%20efforts%20never%20amounted%20to%20any%20major%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president's%20campaign%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%20But%20his%20apparent%20reversal%20on%20open%20primaries%20is%20quite%20simply%20yet%20another%20sign%20of%20his%20hostile%20takeover%20of%20the%20GOP.%20Trump%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20outsider%20now.%20And%20as%20such%2C%20he%20sees%20little%20need%20for%20such%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-nikki-haley-new-hampshire-open-primary-electorate-gop-2024-2024-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705613036000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a990f043bb77284b9e4558%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-nikki-haley-new-hampshire-open-primary-electorate-gop-2024-2024-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20president%20ran%20away%20in%20open%20primary%20contests%20in%202016.%20Now%2C%20he%20no%20longer%20loves%20the%20process%20that%20fuels%20his%20rise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-nikki-haley-new-hampshire-open-primary-electorate-gop-2024-2024-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fusion%20Entertainment%20Signs%20%E2%80%98Ghostlight%E2%80%99%20Star%20Keith%26nbsp%3BKupferer%20Ahead%20of%20Sundance%20Premiere%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705612937000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FKeith-Kupferer-e17