ctorate%20is%20examining%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20response%20to%20the%20fourth%20summons%20for%20questioning%2C%20officials%20have%20told%20NDTV.%20A%20Chief%20Minister%20can%20be%20issued%20a%20non-bailable%20warrant%20and%20arrested%20after%20evading%20summons%20thrice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20evaded%20summons%20four%20times%2C%20refusing%20to%20present%20himself%20before%20probing%20agency%20in%20the%20alleged%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam.%20He%20has%20termed%20summons%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20immunity%20provided%20to%20a%20sitting%20chief%20minister%20under%20law.%20Immunity%20is%20only%20provided%20to%20the%20President%20or%20the%20Governor%20of%20a%20state%2C%20so%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20can%20be%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20still%20examining%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20reply.%20It%20is%20also%20considering%20whether%20a%20questionnaire%20can%20be%20sent%20to%20him%20or%20his%20statement%20can%20be%20recorded%20in%20his%20office%20like%20that%20of%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20illegal%20mining%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20summons%20issued%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20under%20Section%2050%20of%20PMLA%20and%20under%20this%20section%20distinction%20between%20accused%20and%20the%20witness%20is%20not%20there.%20His%20legal%20team%20knows%20that%20but%20they%20still%20have%20asked%20us%20to%20specify%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20probe%20agency%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20asked%20them%20to%20specify%20whether%20he%20has%20been%20called%20as%20a%20witness%20or%20an%20accused.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20deposed%20before%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20in%20same%20case%20last%20year%2C%20when%20the%20agency%20recorded%20his%20statement%20under%20Section%20161%20of%20the%20CrPc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20this%20Section%2C%20a%20statement%20is%20recorded%20as%20a%20witness%2C%20so%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20went.%20But%20under%20PMLA%2C%20this%20distinction%20is%20not%20defined.%20That%20is%20why%20he%20is%20not%20appearing%20before%20the%20ED.%20Also%2C%20his%20legal%20team%20knows%20that%20any%20statement%20he%20makes%20will%20be%20admissible%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20senior%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20skipped%20the%20three%20previous%20summons%20on%20November%202%2C%20December%2022%2C%20and%20on%20January%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%202%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20first%20summons%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20travelled%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20elections%20to%20address%20a%20rally.%20He%20alleged%20that%20the%20ED%20was%20acting%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20malign%20his%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2022%2C%20he%20was%20in%20Punjab%20on%20a%20meditation%20retreat.%20On%20January%203%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20cited%20preparations%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls%20for%20three%20seats%20in%20the%20Capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20name%20has%20figured%20in%20investigations.%20The%20probe%2C%20they%20claimed%2C%20substantiate%20that%20money%20received%20from%20kickbacks%20was%20used%20by%20AAP%20in%20Goa%20elections.%20AAP%20has%20called%20the%20entire%20case%20politically%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20will%20record%20the%20statement%20of%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20on%20January%2020%20at%20his%20officer%20in%20Ranchi.%20Mr%20Soren%20has%20evaded%20seven%20summons%20and%20two%20notices%20sent%20to%20him%20by%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705603680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtv