Yatra%20will%20cover%206%2C713%20km%20in%2067%20days%20while%20passing%20through%20110%20districts%20in%2015%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705600200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F98eqcvt_rahul-gandhi-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra_625x300_18_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-against-rahul-gandhi-led-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-over-route-deviation-in-assam-4888284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20FIR%20was%20registered%20against%20the%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%20and%20its%20chief%20organiser%20KB%20Byju%20for%20allegedly%20deviating%20from%20its%20permitted%20route%20inside%20Jorhat%20town%20in%20Assam%20on%20Thursday%2C%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-against-rahul-gandhi-led-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-over-route-deviation-in-assam-4888284%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-against-rahul-gandhi-led-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-over-route-deviation-in-assam-4888284%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-against-rahul-gandhi-led-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-over-route-deviation-in-assam-4888284%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20Davos%20Diaries%3A%20India's%20Emergence%20And%20Quest%20For%20Global%20Trust%20-%20Gautam%20Adani%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20heavy%20snowfall%20and%20significant%20traffic%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Davos%20this%20year%2C%20it%20became%20apparent%20that%20opting%20for%20the%20hour's%20helicopter%20flight%20from%20Geneva%20was%20a%20practical%20choice.%20As%20we%20prepared%20to%20board%2C%20I%20met%20our%20pilots%2C%20Hans%20and%20Michael%2C%20two%20youthful%20gentlemen%20seemingly%20in%20their%20twenties.%20The%20helicopter's%20journey%20through%20deep%20layers%20of%20thick%20clouds%2C%20flying%20past%20the%20breathtaking%2C%20snow-capped%20peaks%20of%20the%20Swiss%20Alps%2C%20was%20a%20moment%20of%20reflection.%20Trusting%20our%20safety%20to%20these%20two%20relatively%20young%20and%20unknown%20pilots%20and%20believing%20that%20they%20knew%20how%20to%20navigate%20the%20mountainous%20regions%20full%20of%20peaks%20and%20valleys%20covered%20in%20clouds%20resonated%20deeply%20with%20the%20overarching%20theme%20of%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%202024%3A%20Rebuilding%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20first%20major%20theme%20at%20WEF%2024%20was%20about%20rebuilding%20trust%2C%20the%20second%20was%20about%20the%20rise%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20start%20with%20defining%20trust.%20It%20is%20the%20fundamental%20element%20that%20significantly%20impacts%20societal%20operations.%20It%20facilitates%20smoother%20interactions%20and%20cooperation%20both%20among%20individuals%20and%20between%20individuals%20and%20nations.%20Highlighting%20the%20impact%20of%20trust%2C%20Professor%20John%20Whitney%20of%20Columbia%20Business%20School%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BDistrust%20doubles%20the%20cost%20of%20doing%20business.%26quot%3B%20This%20profound%20statement%20underscores%20the%20challenge%20that%20the%20world%20now%20faces.%20While%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20quantify%20the%20cost%20of%20mistrust%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20increasing%20lack%20of%20trust%20amongst%20global%20political%20leaders%20is%20now%20imposing%20a%20massive%20direct%20toll%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20my%20discussions%20this%20year%20with%20a%20diverse%20group%20of%20global%20political%20leaders%2C%20business%20executives%2C%20and%20media%20influencers%2C%20I%20observed%20a%20striking%20consensus%2C%20transcending%20geographical%20and%20ideological%20boundaries.%20The%20focus%20has%20quickly%20shifted%20from%20Covid-19%20to%20a%20more%20complex%20array%20of%20issues.%20It%20is%20hard%20to%20deny%20that%20the%20world%20is%20expected%20to%20stay%20preoccupied%20with%20increasing%20geopolitical%20divisions%2C%20escalating%20hostilities%2C%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20multiple%20conflicts%2C%20all%20contributing%20to%20a%20challenging%20global%20environment%20with%20no%20precedent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20this%20complexity%2C%20humanity%20is%20simultaneously%20tackling%20the%20decoupling%20of%20economies%2C%20climate%20change%20challenges%2C%20and%20the%20ethical%20use%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%20In%20today's%20world%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20an%20ironic%20paradox.%20These%20very%20platforms%20that%20were%20designed%20for%20broadening%20understanding%2C%20exchanging%20ideas%2C%20and%20finding%20common%20ground%20are%20increasingly%20becoming%20the%20areas%20of%20polarization.%20This%20trend%20was%20visible%20even%20at%20the%20WEF%2C%20where%20diversity%20of%20thought%20is%20diminishing%20as%20evident%20from%20the%20lack%20of%20presence%20of%20a%20select%20set%20of%20nations%20that%20should%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20dialogues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20view%2C%20we%20are%20up%20against%20a%20prolonged%20phase%20of%20transition%20that%20will%20be%20marked%20by%20deep%20uncertainty.%20This%20current%20environment%20of%20uncertainty%20will%20continue%20to%20create%20a%20fertile%20ground%20for%20the%20escalation%20and%20proliferation%20of%20conflicts.%20More%20than%20ever%2C%20the%20situation%20today%20underscores%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20enhanced%20multilateralism%20and%20international%20cooperation%2C%20which%20can%20be%20done%20only%20through%20the%20consensus%20emerging%20from%20global%20political%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20moving%20on%20to%20the%20theme%20of%20India%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20several%20corporate%20leaders%2C%20media%20thought%20leaders%2C%20and%20executives%20from%20the%20world's%20top%20financial%20institutions.%20The%20general%20consensus%20was%20that%20while%20India%20is%20well%20on%20its%20way%20to%20approaching%20the%20%2430%20trillion%20GDP%20target%20by%202050%2C%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20for%20even%20higher%20growth%2C%20given%20its%20young%20workforce.%20As%20expected%2C%20every%20discussion%20also%20touched%20upon%20the%20advent%20of%20technologies%20like%20AI%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20this%20adding%20further%20momentum%20to%20India's%20growth.%20One%20of%20the%20discussions%20was%20around%20the%20exciting%20potential%20of%20India%20becoming%20the%20AI%20'back%20office'%20of%20the%20world%2C%20something%20to%20watch%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20most%20impactful%20theme%20that%20emerged%20in%20these%20discussions%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20Rebuilding%20Trust%20theme%20of%20the%20conference%2C%20was%20India's%20dramatic%20social%20transformation%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20India%20is%20increasingly%20seen%20as%20filling%20the%20social%20leadership%20vacuum%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20corporate%20leader%20spent%20most%20of%20our%20conversation%20eager%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20direct%20benefit%20transfer%20platform%2C%20enabled%20by%20the%20integration%20of%20Aadhar%2C%20the%20national%20ID%20system%20program%2C%20mobile%20phone%20access%2C%20and%20an%20astounding%20500%20million%20bank%20accounts.%20This%20system%20has%20not%20only%20increased%20government%20liquidity%20but%20has%20also%20empowered%20millions%20of%20Indians%20in%20the%20remotest%20areas%20to%20trust%20the%20system%20and%20receive%20benefits%20without%20middleman%20interference.%20The%20Unified%20Payment%20Platform%20(UPI)%2C%20launched%20by%20the%20government%20less%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20has%20expanded%2C%20with%20several%20overseas%20markets%20now%20accepting%20UPI%20payments.%20The%20word%20he%20used%20to%20describe%20this%20was%20%26quot%3Bunparalleled%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20inclusivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20focus%20on%20sustainability%20and%20its%20role%20in%20building%20trust%20among%20nations%2C%20the%20Solar%20Alliance%20platform%2C%20launched%20by%20the%20Hon'ble%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20in%202015%2C%20was%20a%20key%20topic%20in%20many%20of%20my%20discussions.%20The%20goal%20to%20mobilize%20one%20trillion%20dollars%20in%20investments%20for%20solar%20energy%20solutions%20by%202030%2C%20aiming%20to%20provide%20clean%20energy%20access%20to%20one%20billion%20people%20through%20the%20installation%20of%201%2C000%20GW%20of%20solar%20energy%20capacity%2C%20once%20seemed%20overly%20ambitious.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20massive%20focus%20on%20sustainability%20and%20the%20success%20of%20COP%2028%2C%20it%20appears%20more%20achievable%20than%20ever.%20What%20started%20as%20a%2016-member%20initiative%20is%20now%20a%20117-member%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20where%20global%20leaders%20adopted%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Leaders'%20Declaration%20(covering%20the%20topics%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20health%2C%20trade%2C%20digital%20economy%2C%20terrorism%2C%20and%20women%20empowerment)%2C%20came%20up%20with%20almost%20all%20leaders%20telling%20me%20that%20this%20was%20the%20best%20G20%20ever.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20remarkable%20achievements%20of%20the%20summit%20was%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20African%20Union%20as%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20a%20move%20initiated%20by%20India.%20This%20decision%20is%20a%20historic%20milestone%20for%20Africa%20and%20the%20broader%20Global%20South%2C%20strengthening%20our%20collective%20voice%20and%20representation%20to%20have%20trust%20in%20global%20governance%20and%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20leave%20Davos%2C%20I%20reflect%20on%20the%20thought%20that%20this%20is%20what%20Rebuilding%20Trust%20should%20be%20all%20about.%20Patriotic%20as%20it%20may%20sound%2C%20India's%20message%20and%20the%20actions%20it%20has%20taken%20resonate%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20multilateralism%20and%20inclusiveness%2C%20perhaps%20like%20no%20other%20nation%20today.%20This%20was%20the%20Davos%20where%20my%20fellow%20countrymen%20in%20attendance%20would%20have%20left%20with%20their%20heads%20a%20little%20higher%20than%20usual.%20No%20better%20time%20to%20be%20an%20Indian!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Gautam%20Adani%20is%20Chairman%2C%20Adani%20Group)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705600140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F391b8ecg_gautam-adani-davos_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fdavos-diaries-indias-emergence-and-quest-for-global-trust-gautam-adani-4888528%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Given%20the%20heavy%20snowfall%20and%20significant%20traffic%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Davos%20this%20year%2C%20it%20became%20apparent%20that%20opting%20for%20the%20hour's%20helicopter%20flight%20from%20Geneva%20was%20a%20practical%20choice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fdavos-diaries-indias-emergence-and-quest-for-global-trust-gautam-adani-4888528%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fdavos-diaries-indias-emergence-and-quest-for-global-trust-gautam-adani-4888528%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fdavos-diaries-indias-emergence-and-quest-for-global-trust-gautam-adani-4888528%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ira%20kisses%20Nupur%2C%20dances%20with%20Aamir%3A%20WATCH%20video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705600087000