ious%20of%20our%20responsibility%20to%20provide%20safety%20to%20our%20people%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20month%20an%20Israeli%20financial%20daily%20said%20the%20country%20planned%20to%20bring%20in%20about%2070%2C000%20foreign%20workers%20from%20China%2C%20India%20and%20elsewhere%20to%20boost%20its%20construction%20sector%2C%20which%20has%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%20since%20the%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20operatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20National%20Skills%20Development%20Corporation%20canvassed%20in%20recent%20weeks%20for%20workers%20to%20live%20and%20work%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20at%20the%20camp%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivek%20Sharma%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20mason%2C%20said%20he%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20risks%20in%20Israel%20from%20the%20conflict%20but%20was%20willing%20to%20take%20the%20risk%20if%20he%20could%20earn%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20am%20aware%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20but%20I%20can%20earn%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20a%20short%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vivek%20Sharma%2C%20who%20estimates%20he%20could%20end%20up%20earning%20more%20than%20a%20million%20Indian%20rupees%20(%2412%2C000)%20by%20working%20in%20Israel%20for%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20take%20me%20at%20least%20five%20years%20to%20earn%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20data%20shows%20about%2013%20million%20Indian%20nationals%20work%20overseas%20as%20labourers%2C%20professionals%2C%20and%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20India%20signed%20an%20agreement%20last%20year%20to%20allow%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20Indians%20to%20work%20in%20the%20Jewish%20state%20in%20the%20nursing%20and%20construction%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%