%2F06172005%2Fpic-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffact-check-ram-mandir-is-being-built-at-the-same-site-where-babri-masjid-once-stood-not-3-km-away%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20social%20media%20users%2C%20including%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%2C%20have%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20is%20being%20built%203%20kilometres%20away%20from%20the%20site%20of%20the%20now-demolished%20Babri%20Masjid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffact-check-ram-mandir-is-being-built-at-the-same-site-where-babri-masjid-once-stood-not-3-km-away%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Couple's%20Daughter%20Dies%20From%20Rare%20Disease%2C%20Then%20They%20Made%20Her%20Into%20Stones%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20heartbreaking%20loss%20of%20their%2015-month-old%20daughter%2C%20an%20Idaho%20couple%2C%20Kaylee%20and%20Jake%20Massey%2C%20chose%20a%20distinctive%20and%20meaningful%20approach%20to%20ensure%20the%20presence%20of%20their%20late%20little%20girl%20in%20their%20home.%C2%A0In%20April%202023%2C%20the%20couple%20endured%20the%20unimaginable%20when%20Poppy%2C%20their%20daughter%20diagnosed%20with%20the%20rare%20genetic%20disorder%20TBCD%20at%209%20months%20old%2C%20died.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20she%20was%20born%2C%20we%20knew%20absolutely%20nothing.%20She%20was%20just%20perfect%20to%20us.%20When%20she%20was%20around%204%20months%20old%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20her%20vision%20wasn't%20developing%20properly.%20And%20so%20after%20some%20doctor's%20appointments%20and%20ophthalmologist%20appointments%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20she%20needed%20an%20MRI%20on%20her%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Massey%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fcouple-daughter-dies-rare-disease-turn-her-into-stones-exclusive-8424374%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPeople%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20she%20was%205%20months%20old%20is%20when%20we%20finally%20got%20that%2C%20and%20the%20MRI%20showed%20that%20the%20centre%20part%20of%20her%20brain%2C%20the%20corpus%20callosum%2C%20hadn't%20developed%20properly%2C%20if%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%2C%20we%20just%20continued%20to%20get%20diagnosis%20after%20diagnosis%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20conclusive%20diagnosis...%20After%20doing%20the%20most%20advanced%20genetic%20tests%20on%20the%20market%2C%20we%20got%20the%20most%20horrific%20news%20to%20find%20out%20that%20she%20had%20a%20genetic%20disorder%20that%20I%20think%20at%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20the%2038th%20child%20in%20the%20world%20diagnosed%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continues.%20%26quot%3BThe%20geneticists%20had%20never%20even%20heard%20of%20it%20before...%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20realized%20what%20a%20severe%20diagnosis%20it%20was.%20We%20were%20just%20really%20naive%20in%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20before%20their%20daughter's%20death%2C%20the%20infant%20developed%20a%20respiratory%20infection.%20She%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20panicky%20because%20I%20felt%20like%20Poppy%20couldn't%20breathe%2C%20and%20we%20were%20so%20heightened%20with%20Poppy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20informed%20the%20couple%20that%20Poppy%20had%20pneumonia%20in%20her%20lungs%20and%20also%20tested%20positive%20for%20a%20respiratory%20infection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20other%20kiddos%20with%20this%20TBCD%20genetic%20condition%20that%20have%20had%20pneumonia%20and%20hospital%20stays%2C%20and%20they're%20there%20for%20a%20week%20and%20they%20go%20home.%20And%20so%20we%20had%20only%20heard%20from%20these%20other%20families%20that%20they%20get%20over%20it%2C%20and%20then%20they%20go%20home%2C%20and%20they%20live%20to%20be%203%20to%205%20years%20old.%20We%20were%20blindsided%20that%20her%20body%20couldn't%20take%20it%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%2C%20Kaylee%20and%20Jake%20received%20the%20news%20that%20they%20had%20to%20transfer%20Poppy%20to%20the%20Intensive%20Care%20Unit%20(ICU).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%20it%20in%20such%20a%20positive%20way.%20They%20said%20it%20like%2C%20'They%20have%20such%20better%20equipment%20over%20there%2C%20Poppy%20will%20get%20the%20care%20she%20needs.'%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20right%20as%20we%20were%20pushing%20her%20bed%20into%20her%20new%20room%20in%20the%20ICU...and%20just%20about%20right%20as%20we%20parked%20her%20bed%20is%20when%20her%20eyes%20kind%20of%20looked%20up%20at%20me%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20Poppy%2C%20your%20eyes%20are%20open.'%20And%20then%20her%20heart%20just%20stopped.%20And%20so%20immediately%2C%20the%20charge%20nurse%20started%20doing%20CPR%20and%20people%20were%20just%20yelling%2C%20'call%20code%2C'%20and%20frantic%20chaos%20ensued%20at%20that%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20probably%20around%206%3A00%20a.m.%20when%20she%20coded%2C%20and%20so%20we%20had%20about%20five%20hours%20with%20her.%20We%20called%20our%20parents%2C%20who%20were%20watching%20our%20other%20two%20children%2C%20and%20they%20were%20able%20to%20come%20and%20say%20their%20goodbyes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20shares.%20%26quot%3BWe%20felt%20it%20was%20very%20important%20to%20have%20Rosie%20and%20Peter%20there%20to%20say%20goodbye%20...%20we%20had%20to%20tell%20them%2C%20'Your%20sister's%20going%20to%20die%20today.'%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20moment%20arrived%20for%20Kaylee%20and%20Jake%20to%20decide%20on%20Poppy's%20remains%2C%20the%20couple%20chose%20an%20option%20that%20was%20entirely%20new%20to%20them%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpartingstone.com%2Fblogs%2Fnews%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EParting%20Stones%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20sitting%20in%20the%20funeral%20home%20and%20they%20handed%20us%20a%20catalogue%20for%20us%20to%20decide%20what%20to%20do%20with%20our%20daughter%2C%20and%20it%20was%20just%20so%20horrible%20to%20flip%20through%20these%20pages%20and%20have%20to%20pick%20out%20an%20urn%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20we%20wanted%20cremation%20because%20we%20wanted%20her%20ashes%20home%20with%20us.%20Having%20two%20young%20kids%20at%20home%2C%20we%20did%20not%20want%20anything%20in%20our%20home%20that%20our%20kids%20would%20be%20fearful%20of%2C%20fearful%20of%20breaking%2C%20fearful%20of%20looking%20at%2C%20and%20we%20felt%20like%20an%20urn%20might%20have%20that%20presence%20in%20our%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20feel%20like%20that%20was%20right%20for%20our%20family%2C%20but%20honestly%2C%20no%20option%20felt%20right%20for%20our%20family.%20We%20were%20just%20flipping%20through%20this%20catalogue%2C%20and%20there%20was%20this%20picture%20of%20these%20really%20pretty%20stones%2C%20and%20we're%20kind%20of%20a%20nature%20family.%20We%20like%20to%20go%20outside%20and%20do%20things.%20And%20I%20remember%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20both%20kind%20of%20stopped%20and%20looked%20at%20that%20page%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20brought%20the%20catalogue%20home%2C%20and%20we%20thought%20about%20it%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20before%20we%20gave%20them%20our%20answer.%20And%20it%20felt%20like%20if%20all%20the%20options%20were%20bad%2C%20this%20one%20felt%20like%20the%20least%20bad%20option.%20We%20chose%20what%20was%20least%20bad%20for%20us%2C%20and%20we%20also%20tried%20to%20put%20Rosie%20and%20Peter%20first.%20What%20would%20they%20be%20most%20comfortable%20around%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20later%2C%20the%20family%20received%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20box%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20handwritten%20note.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20beautifully%20said.%20It%20was%20something%20like%2C%20'Thank%20you%20for%20entrusting%20us%20with%20your%20daughter.%20It's%20been%20an%20honour%20to%20have%20her%20in%20our%20care.'%20It%20felt%20so%20personal%2C%20and%20I%20remember%20opening%20that%20card%20and%20just%20feeling%20like%20these%20people%20cared%20about%20my%20daughter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continued%20to%20open%20up%20these%20little%20bags%20that%20had%20the%20stones%20in%20them%2C%20and%20I%20remember%20initially%2C%20the%20stones%20were%20so%20beautiful.%20They're%20white%20with%20little%20specks%20of%20yellow%20in%20them%2C%20and%20they%20say%20that%20they%20don't%20do%20anything%20to%20the%20ashes%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaylee%20explains.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20little%20specks%20of%20yellow%20are%2C%20but%20they%20feel%20like%20such%20a%20little%20special%20gift.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705596660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ft8av81f_kaylee-and-jake-massey_625x300_18_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-couples-15-month-old-daughter-dies-from-rare-disease-then-they-made-her-into-stones-4888289%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20doctors%20informed%20the%20couple%20that%20Poppy%20had%20pneumonia%20in%20her%20lungs%20and%20also%20tested%20positive%20for%20a%20respiratory%20infection.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-couples-15-month-old-daughter-dies-from-rare-disease-then-they-made-her-into-stones-4888289%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-couples-15-month-old-daughter-dies-from-rare-disease-then-they-made-her-into-stones-4888289%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-couples-15-month-old-daughter-dies-from-rare-disease-then-they-made-her-into-stones-4888289%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%20signs%20agreement%20to%20purchase%20400%20Tomahawk%20missiles%20as%20US%20envoy%20lauds%20its%20defense%20buildup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705595699000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106965935%2Cimgsize-11016.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-signs-agreement-to-purchase-400-tomahawk-missiles-as-us-envoy-lauds-its-defense-buildup%2Farticleshow%2F106965894.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106965894.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-signs-agreement-to-purchase-400-tomahawk-missiles-as-us-envoy-lauds-its-defense-buildup%2Farticleshow%2F106965894.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-signs-agreement-to-purchase-400-tomahawk-missiles-as-us-envoy-lauds-its-defense-buildup%2Famp_articleshow%2F106965894.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-signs-agreement-to-purchase-400-tomahawk-missiles-as-us-envoy-lauds-its-defense-buildup%2Famp_articleshow%2F106965894.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Are%20Ladakh%2C%20Kashmir%20So%20Warm%20In%20Peak%20Winter%3F%20Scientists%20Explain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20western%20Himalayan%20region%20logged%20an%2080%20per%20cent%20precipitation%20deficit%20in%20December%2C%20and%20January%20so%20far%20has%20been%20almost%20dry%2C%20with%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20attributing%20it%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20active%20western%20disturbances%20this%20winter%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20active%20western%20disturbances%20%E2%80%94%20weather%20systems%20that%20originate%20in%20the%20Mediterranean%20region%20and%20bring%20unseasonal%20rainfall%20to%20northwest%20India%20%E2%80%94%20is%20also%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20blinding%20layer%20of%20fog%20persisting%20over%20the%20plains%20in%20the%20region%20since%20December%2025%2C%20the%20IMD%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20precipitation%20deficit%20is%20likely%20to%20impact%20freshwater%20availability%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20region%2C%20further%20affecting%20horticulture%20and%20agricultural%20production%2C%20said%20Sonam%20Lotus%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20meteorological%20centre%20in%20Leh%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJanuary%20is%20peak%20winter%20but%20surprisingly%2C%20it%20is%20so%20warm%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20Kashmir%20that%20crops%20are%20blooming%20early%2C%20and%20this%20is%20very%20worrying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaihana%20Habib%20Kanth%2C%20Dean%20(Agriculture)%20Sher-e-Kashmir%20University%20of%20Agricultural%20Sciences%20and%20Technology%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20the%20snowfall%20in%20the%20Chillai%20Kalan%20period%20(December%2021%20to%20January%2029)%20is%20the%20only%20freshwater%20source%20for%20the%20region%20before%20the%20southwest%20monsoon%20sets%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20prolonged%20dry%20spell%20has%20reduced%20the%20water%20level%20in%20the%20rivers%20and%20streams%20in%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20authored%20by%20IMD%20scientists%20Krishna%20Mishra%2C%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20and%20RK%20Jenamani%2C%20maximum%20temperatures%20have%20been%20below%20normal%20by%205-8%20degrees%20Celsius%20over%20the%20northern%20plains%20since%20December%2029%2C%20with%20a%20respite%20on%20January%207-8%20due%20to%20a%20western%20disturbance.%20Minimum%20temperatures%20have%20been%20below%204%20degrees%20Celsius%20at%20many%20stations%20in%20the%20region%20from%20January%2012%20to%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20very%20dense%20fog%20has%20been%20persisting%20over%20the%20plains%20of%20northwest%20India%20since%20December%2025%2C%20reaching%20its%20maximum%20intensity%20and%20duration%20on%20January%2014%20when%20visibility%20dropped%20to%20zero%20metres%20over%20the%20entire%20northern%20plains%20from%20Amritsar%20to%20Dibrugarh%20across%20Haryana%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20severe%20weather%20over%20north%20India%20is%20primarily%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20active%20western%20disturbances%20over%20northwest%20India%20during%20December%20and%20January.%20Generally%2C%205-7%20wester%20disturbances%20impact%20the%20region%20during%20these%20months.%20The%20region%20has%20not%20seen%20any%20strong%20western%20disturbance%20this%20winter%20so%20far%2C%20the%20scientists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20western%20disturbances%20affected%20the%20country%2C%20one%20in%20December%20and%20another%20in%20January%2C%20but%20their%20impact%20remained%20confined%20to%20Gujarat%2C%20north%20Maharashtra%2C%20east%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20western%20Himalayan%20Region%20has%20received%20very%20little%20precipitation%20(rain%2Fsnow)%20during%20the%20month%20of%20December%2C%20roughly%20about%2080%20per%20cent%20less%20than%20normal.%20Similarly%2C%20there%20has%20been%20almost%20nil%20precipitation%20in%20the%20region%20in%20January%20so%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20severe%20weather%20is%20mainly%20due%20to%20three%20reasons%3A%20lack%20of%20active%20western%20disturbances%20over%20northwest%20India%2C%20prevailing%20El-Nino%20conditions%2C%20and%20a%20strong%20jet%20stream%2C%20the%20scientists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BFog%20formation%20requires%20three%20conditions%3A%20weak%20low-level%20winds%2C%20moisture%2C%20and%20overnight%20cooling.%20Strong%20western%20disturbances%2C%20characterized%20by%20strong%20winds%20and%20precipitation%2C%20disrupt%20these%20conditions.%26quot%3B%20Strong%20jet%20streams%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20bands%20of%20strong%20wind%20that%20generally%20blow%20from%20west%20to%20east%20all%20across%20the%20globe%20and%20impact%20weather%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20prevailing%20over%20north%20India%20for%20the%20last%20five%20days.%20It%20is%20leading%20to%20subsidence%20of%20cold%20air%20and%20enhancing%20cold%20wave%2Fcold%20day%20conditions%20over%20the%20region.%20These%20conditions%20are%20likely%20to%20continue%20over%20the%20next%20five%20days%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20active%20western%20disturbances%20can%20also%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20prevailing%20El-Nino%20conditions%2C%20abnormal%20warming%20of%20surface%20waters%20in%20the%20central%20Pacific%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20El-Nino%20years%2C%20there%20are%20fewer%20cold%20wave%20days%20over%20north%20India%20during%20December%20and%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705595460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkj7noajk_gulmarg-no-snow-pti_625x300_18_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-are-ladakh-kashmir-so-warm-in-peak-winter-scientists-explain-4887911%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20western%20Himalayan%20region%20logged%20an%2080%20per%20cent%20precipitation%20deficit%20in%20December%2C%20and%20January%20so%20far%20has%20been%20almost%20dry%2C%20with%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20attributing%20it%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20active%20western%20disturbances%20this%20winter%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-are-ladakh-kashmir-so-warm-in-peak-winter-scientists-explain-4887911%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-are-ladakh-kashmir-so-warm-in-peak-winter-scientists-explain-4887911%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-are-ladakh-kashmir-so-warm-in-peak-winter-scientists-explain-4887911%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAs%20Long%20As...%26quot%3B%3A%20Dravid's%20Verdict%20On%20'Controversial%20Run'%20During%20Super%20Over%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPlaying%20down%20the%20on-field%20controversy%20around%20a%20moment%20during%20the%20first%20super%20over%20of%20the%20pulsating%20third%20T20I%20against%20Afghanistan%20at%20the%20Chinnaswamy%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20India%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20the%20game%26quot%3B.%20India%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20seen%20remonstrating%20with%20an%20on-field%20umpire%20after%20Afghan%20all-rounder%20Mohammed%20Nabi%20ran%20byes%20off%20a%20deflected%20throw%20during%20the%20first%20super%20over%20of%20the%20T20I%20on%20Wednesday.%20That%20moment%20was%20one%20of%20many%20that%20made%20the%20nail-biting%20contest%20one%20for%20the%20ages.%20The%20hosts%2C%20however%2C%20survived%20a%20mighty%20scare%20from%20the%20visitors%20to%20seal%20the%20contest%20in%20the%20second%20super%20over%20and%20ensure%20a%20series%20sweep.%20Nabi%20and%20Rahmanullah%20Gurbaz%20ran%20byes%20after%20Sanju%20Samson's%20throw%20struck%20the%20former%20and%20deflected%20off%20him%20to%20the%20outfield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20his%20take%20on%20the%20incident%2C%20Dravid%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20fine.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20Sometimes%20you%20get%20frustrated%20that%20it%20happens%2C%20but%20it's%20fair%20enough%2C%20all%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20It%20hit%20the%20non-striker%20and%20then%20it%20moved%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20fine%20and%20you%20can%20run%20for%20those.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid%20went%20on%20to%20compare%20the%20incident%20with%20an%20instance%20that%20took%20place%20during%20the%20first%20T20I%20of%20the%20series%20when%20the%20hosts%20picked%20up%20a%20run%20in%20a%20similar%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20first%20T20%2C%20I%20think%20there%20was%20an%20incident%20where%20the%20ball%20hit%20the%20bat%20of%20one%20of%20our%20batsmen%20and%20we%20took%20a%20run%20as%20well.%20So%20I%20think%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20read%20into%20it%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20nothing%20in%20the%20rules%20that%20stops%20you%20from%20actually%20taking%20those%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20Dravid%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArguments%20can%20happen%20at%20the%20end%20of%20tight%20games.%20I%20think%20when%20you%20play%20for%20your%20country%2C%20there%20is%20so%20much%20passion%20and%20emotion%20and%20I%20think%20it%20is%20incredible%20that%20even%20in%20dead%20rubber%20games%20when%20it%20gets%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20the%20competitiveness%20and%20passion%20come%20out.%20As%20long%20as%20it%20doesn't%20cross%20the%20line%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20we%20have%20match%20referees%20to%20look%20at%20these%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Dravid%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20was%20quite%20animated%20after%20Afghanistan%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20run%20after%20the%20ball%20struck%20the%20player.%20Even%20Virat%20Kohli%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20ball%20had%20struck%20Nabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid%20opined%20that%20such%20a%20display%20of%20emotions%20was%20normal%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20that%20passion%20and%20emotion%20is%20really%20important.%20It%20shows%20how%20much%20the%20players%20care.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Afghanistan%20managed%20to%20match%20India's%20212%20with%20a%20collective%20performance.%20The%20match%20went%20to%20super%20over%20which%20saw%20the%20first%20one%20ending%20on%20level%20terms%20forcing%20the%20game%20to%20move%20to%20the%20second%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit's%20impressive%20strikes%20and%20Ravi%20Bishnoi's%20composure%20with%20the%20ball%20helped%20India%20clinch%20the%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705595400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fdro6h43g_sc_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-afghanistan-t20i-2024%2Findia-vs-afghanistan-3rd-t20i-as-long-as-rahul-dravids-verdict-on-controversial-run-during-super-over-4885173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20seen%20remonstrating%20with%20an%20on-field%20umpire%20after%20Afghan%20all-rounder%20Mohammed%20Nabi%20ran%20byes%20off%20a%20deflected%20throw%20during%20the%20first%20Super%20Over.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20vs%20China%3A%20Explaining%20Military%20Strength%20Beyond%20Numbers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20ranked%20as%20the%20fourth%20strongest%20military%20in%20the%20world%2C%20just%20after%20China%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalfirepower.com%2Fcountries-comparison-detail.php%3Fcountry1%3Dindia%26country2%3Dchina%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Firepower%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20analyses%20data%20based%20on%20factors%20that%20determine%20a%20nation's%20war-fighting%20capability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20the%20biggest%20spender%20on%20defence%20in%20Asia.%20In%20the%20financial%20year%202023-2024%2C%20India%20allocated%20%2473.9%20billion%2C%20while%20China%20reserved%20%24229%20Billion%20of%20its%20budget%20for%20the%20military.%20The%20Centre%20for%20Strategic%20and%20Investment%20Studies%20(CSIS)%2C%20a%20US-based%20think%20tank%2C%20has%20said%20China's%20defence%20budget%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20published%20figures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Global%20Firepower%20Index%2C%20China's%20defence%20budget%20is%20the%20second%20highest%20globally%20and%20India%20stands%20at%20number%20four.%20The%20huge%20gap%20between%20India%20and%20China%20should%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20difference%20in%20the%20size%20of%20GDPs.%20India%20is%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%20and%20spends%2013%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20annual%20budget%20on%20defence.%20Meanwhile%2C%20China%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%201.45%20million%20active%20personnel%20and%20China%20has%202.03%20million%20soldiers%20in%20the%20PLA%20Army%2C%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force.%20Viewing%20the%20imbalance%20in%20power%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20military%20through%20statistics%20is%20myopic%2C%20considering%20factors%20like%20operational%20deployment%2C%20experience%20and%20nuclear%20capabilities%20of%20both%20nations%20are%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fm1j5a4lo_india-vs-china-_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmy%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20was%20the%20armed%20wing%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20(CPC)%20during%20the%20civil%20war.%20When%20Mao%20Zedong%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20PLA%20became%20the%20national%20army%20and%20the%20Air%20Force%20and%20the%20Navy%20were%20its%20two%20other%20components.%20With%20more%20active%20personnel%20and%20a%20strong%20domestic%20industrial%20complex%2C%20the%20PLA%20has%20an%20advantage%20over%20the%20Indian%20Army%20in%20terms%20of%20statistics%2C%20but%20the%20world's%20two%20strong%20armies%2C%20with%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20fighting%20a%20long%20war%20is%20highly%20unlikely.%20Any%20future%20armed%20conflict%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20limited%20to%20the%20border%20like%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20clash%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-02%2Ft0ces1ts_galwan-valley-clash_625x300_19_February_21.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20reorganised%20its%20military%20into%20seven%20commands%20based%20on%20geography%20and%20operational%20needs.%20Christopher%20K%20Colley%20and%20Prashant%20Hosur%20Sahas%2C%20in%20their%20research%20paper%2C%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1177%2F2347797021993962%23table2-2347797021993962%5C%22%3EIndia-China%20and%20Their%20War-Making%20Capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E'%2C%20explain%20the%20advantage%20Indian%20troops%20have%20at%20high%20altitudes.%20The%20Western%20Theatre%20Command%20of%20China%20is%20the%20largest%20of%20the%20seven%20commands%20and%20is%20responsible%20for%20operations%20along%20the%20LAC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%202.5%20lakh%20PLA%20troops%20are%20under%20the%20command%20but%20only%2040%2C000%20are%20in%20Tibet%2C%20the%20rest%20are%20deployed%20in%20the%20Xinjiang%2C%20Sichuan%20and%20Chongqing%20regions.%20Quick%20mobilization%20is%20vital%20and%20at%20high%20altitudes%2C%20speedy%20deployment%20with%20little%20to%20no%20time%20for%20acclimatization%20can%20result%20in%20high-altitude%20sickness.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F06%2F17%2Fasia%2Findia-china-military-comparison-hnk-intl-scli%2Findex.html%5C%22%3EBrad%20Lendon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20military%20affairs%20expert%2C%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20maintains%20an%20edge%20in%20high-altitude%20mountainous%20environments%2C%20such%20as%20the%20one%20where%20the%202020%20face-off%20is%20taking%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%20portions%20of%20Chinese%20troops%20are%20not%20stationed%20at%20high%20altitudes%2C%20while%20the%20Indian%20forces%20have%20more%20experience%20in%20high-altitude%20operations%20and%20are%20deployed%20close%20to%20the%20border.%20The%20Himalayan%20plateau%20is%20uneven%20with%20variations%20in%20elevation%20and%20puts%20the%20PLA%20at%20a%20disadvantage%20due%20to%20its%20positioning.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcis.mit.edu%2Fpublications%2Fanalysis-opinion%2F2020%2Ftension-high-altitude-higher-logistical-and-physiological%5C%22%3E%20Doklam%20standoff%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20PLA's%20single%20approach%20to%20the%20region%20through%20the%20Chumbi%20Valley%20was%20within%20Indian%20artillery%20range%20and%20before%20the%20standoff%20even%20began%2C%20more%20Indian%20troops%20were%20already%20present%20in%20the%20region%20as%20part%20of%20forward%20deployments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20military%20has%20had%20no%20combat%20experience%20since%20it%20invaded%20Vietnam%20in%201979.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20managed%20to%20mobilize%20at%20least%20200%2C000%20troops%20during%20the%201999%20Kargil%20conflict%20to%20fight%20Pakistan%20at%20high%20altitude.%20Indian%20troops%20are%20stationed%20at%20the%20Siachen%20Glacier%20and%20force%20commanders%20have%20rich%20combat%20experience%20because%20of%20the%20counter-terrorism%20operations%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAir%20Force%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%203%2C304%20aircraft%2C%20while%20India%20has%202%2C296%20in%20all%20the%20forces.%20China's%20J-20%20Chengdu%20is%20its%20fifth-generation%20stealth%20fighter.%20India%20only%20has%204.5%20generation%20fighters%20like%20Rafale%20and%20Tejas%20MK1A%20won't%20be%20a%20fifth%20generation.%20Most%20of%20the%20IAF%20fighter%20jets%20in%20the%20current%20fleet%20were%20acquired%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20and%20'90s%20and%20are%20still%20in%20service%20and%20induction%20has%20been%20slow.%20The%20Tejas%20programme%20was%20envisioned%20in%201985%20and%20the%20induction%20took%20several%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fmo3ng00g_light-combat-aircraft-tejas_625x300_30_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PLAAF%20has%20fewer%20fighter%20jets%20positioned%20in%20Tibet%20compared%20to%20the%20IAF.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.belfercenter.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2020-03%2Findia-china-postures%2FChina%2520India%2520Postures.pdf%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Kennedy%20School%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Belfer%20Centre%2C%20around%20180%20Chinese%20aircraft%20are%20present%20under%20the%20Western%20Command%20and%20their%20responsibility%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20defence%20of%20LAC%20along%20India%20but%20other%20nations%20like%20Mongolia%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20Myanmar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20270%20fighter%20jets%20positioned%20in%20different%20commands%20to%20counter%20China.%20If%20we%20ignore%20the%20difference%20in%20posturing%2C%20the%20PLAAF%20jets%20are%20not%20located%20close%20to%20the%20border%20and%20for%20any%20attack%20operation%2C%20the%20jets%20have%20to%20choose%20between%20fuel%20or%20payloads%20for%20long%20sorties%20due%20to%20long%20combat%20radius%20compared%20to%20the%20IAF.%20An%20Indian%20MiG-21%20shooting%20down%20Pakistan's%20F-16%20in%202019%20is%20the%20latest%20incident%20to%20demonstrate%20an%20IAF%20pilot's%20combat%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20argument%20of%20combat%20experience%20enters%20the%20discussion%20when%20India%20and%20China's%20military%20capabilities%20are%20compared.%20The%20argument%20holds%20some%20relevance%20as%20experience%20helps%20in%20survivability%20and%20performance.%20In%20an%20article%20on%20RAND%2C%20Timothy%20Heath%2C%20a%20defence%20researcher%2C%20writes%20that%20though%20China%20has%20a%20high-tech%20arsenal%2C%20its%20ability%20to%20use%20these%20weapons%20is%20unclear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20a%20fleet%20strength%20of%20730%2C%20which%20includes%2061%20submarines%20and%203%20Helicopter%20Carriers.%20India%20has%20a%20fleet%20strength%20of%20294%20with%2018%20subs%20and%200%20Helo%20carriers.%20The%20development%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Navy%20has%20been%20significant%20and%20worth%20appreciating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20growth%20was%20aimed%20at%20countering%20the%20US%20Navy%20against%20Taiwan%2C%20but%20China's%20interest%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20started%20a%20decade%20ago%20with%20its%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20are%20blue%20water%20navies%2C%20meaning%20they%20can%20operate%20globally%20with%20their%20aircraft%20carriers.%20Its%20objectives%20would%20be%20to%20defend%20the%20'Sea%20Links%20of%20Communication'%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20(IOR)%20and%20any%20conflict%20would%20not%20occur%20in%20the%20Pacific%20but%20in%20the%20IOR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20QUAD%20alliance%20between%20India%2C%20Australia%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Japan%20aims%20for%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%20China%20has%20deep%20interests%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20and%20a%20conflict%20with%20Indian%20Navy%20would%20happen%20in%20the%20IOR%2C%20implying%20that%20the%20Chinese%20Navy%20has%20to%20move%20its%20fleet%20from%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20toward%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%2C%20giving%20Indian%20Navy%20time%20to%20choke%20transit%20point%20like%20Strait%20of%20Malacca%20and%20get%20support%20from%20QUAD%20partners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705594980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fnfd8fqlc_india-china-ladakh-generic-ndtv-fil-photo_625x300_25_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-vs-china-explaining-military-strength-beyond-numbers-4888129%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20been%20ranked%20as%20the%20fourth%20strongest%20military%20in%20the%20world%2C%20just%20after%20China%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Global%20Firepower%20Index%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20analyses%20data%20based%20on%20factors%20that%20determine%20a%20nation's%20war-fighting%20capability.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-vs-china-explaining-military-strength-beyond-numbers-4888129%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-vs-china-explaining-military-strength-beyond-numbers-4888129%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-vs-china-explaining-military-strength-beyond-numbers-4888129%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20Steel%20To%20Cut%203%2C000%20Jobs%20In%20Wales%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETata%20Steel%20is%20to%20cut%20about%203%2C000%20jobs%20at%20a%20plant%20in%20Wales%2C%20a%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20plan%20said%20Thursday%2C%20as%20the%20industry%20struggles%20to%20finance%20greener%20production%20of%20the%20metal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20will%20on%20Friday%20confirm%20the%20closure%20of%20two%20blast%20furnaces%20at%20the%20Port%20Talbot%20steelworks%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20over%20one-third%20of%20staff%2C%20the%20source%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20for%20comment%2C%20Tata%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bbeen%20engaging%20regularly%20and%20constructively%20with...%20trades%20union%20colleagues%20and%20their%20advisors%20for%20some%20time%20about%20the%20best%20way%20forward%20to%20create%20a%20sustainable%20green%20steel%20future%20for%20Tata%20Steel%20in%20the%20UK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20have%20any%20formal%20announcement%20to%20make%20about%20our%20proposals%20for%20the%20future%2C%20we%20will%20always%20share%20these%20with%20our%20employees%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20the%20UK%20government%20provided%20%C2%A3500%20million%20(%24634%20million)%20to%20fund%20the%20production%20of%20%26quot%3Bgreener%26quot%3B%20steel%20at%20the%20country's%20biggest%20steelworks%2C%20while%20saying%20that%203%2C000%20jobs%20were%20still%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20for%20an%20electric%20furnace%20safeguarded%205%2C000%20of%20the%20more%20than%208%2C000%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPort%20Talbot%20steelworks%20is%20the%20UK's%20single%20biggest%20carbon%20emitter%2C%20and%20the%20government%20has%20been%20looking%20to%20help%20Tata%20Steel%20and%20British%20Steel%2C%20run%20by%20Chinese%20group%20Jingye%2C%20to%20replace%20dirty%20blast%20furnaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conglomerate%20had%20threatened%20to%20shut%20the%20plant%20unless%20it%20received%20state%20aid%20to%20help%20decarbonise%20production%20and%20cut%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20replacing%20the%20coal-powered%20blast%20furnaces%20at%20the%20Port%20Talbot%20site%20would%20reduce%20the%20UK's%20carbon%20emissions%20by%20about%201.5%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20said%20green%20hydrogen%20could%20help%20the%20massively%20polluting%20steel%20industry%2C%20but%20producing%20the%20clean%20energy%20in%20large%20enough%20quantities%20requires%20significant%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20well%20as%20climate%20fallout%2C%20the%20steel%20sector%20has%20seen%20costs%20soar%20amid%20surging%20energy%20prices%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi