n%20party%20has%20its%20own%20chief%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20namely%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Assam.%20These%20yield%20179%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20are%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20best%20bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20has%20its%20CM%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Uttarakhand%20(together%2015%20seats)%2C%20but%20in%20these%20it%20is%20apt%20to%20face%20a%20lively%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%20(48%20seats)%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%20in%20an%20alliance%20government%20and%20could%20win%20about%20half%20the%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%20(28%20seats)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-a-potentially-historic-election%5C%22%3Ethe%20party%20was%20ejected%20from%20office%20by%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20May%20but%20enjoys%20a%20widespread%20presence%2C%20though%20its%20organisational%20abilities%20appear%20to%20have%20suffered%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20stinging%20defeat%20in%20the%20assembly%20election.%20The%20party%20here%20also%20seems%20to%20acutely%20feel%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20acceptable%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FqXohhDbkOUs%3Fsi%3DbGL3W9_rPllpYAX8%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20states%20named%20above%20make%20up%20270%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20543%3B%20that%20is%2C%20about%2050%25%20of%20all%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20best%20category%20of%20179%2C%20where%20the%20party%20seems%20beyond%20effective%20challenge%2C%20it%20had%20won%20nearly%2080-90%25%20of%20the%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20and%20there%20is%20not%20much%20scope%20for%20improvement.%20If%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20context%20of%20these%20states%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20%E2%80%93%20are%20smart%2C%20they%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20snatch%20some%20seats%2C%20but%20not%20many%2C%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20effort%2C%20the%20election%20of%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20%E2%80%93%20a%20stalwart%20figure%20of%20Dalit%20background%20%E2%80%93%20as%20Congress%20president%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-named-chairperson-nitish-kumar-as-convenor-of-india-bloc-report%5C%22%3EINDIA%20coalition%20chairman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20decided%20plus.%20Elsewhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%20including%20the%20other%20states%20where%20the%20BJP%20enjoys%20salience%2C%20the%20Kharge%20factor%20can%20become%20a%20force%20multiplier%20for%20the%20opposition%20grouping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpromise-to-bring-peace-says-rahul-gandhi-as-he-kicks-off-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-from-manipur%5C%22%3Eeast-to-west%20Nyay%20Yatra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recently%20launched%20under%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20supported%20by%20the%20INDIA%20parties%2C%20may%20also%20be%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20key%20booster%2C%20including%20in%20UP%2C%20which%20sends%20up%20the%20most%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20and%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20largely%20through%20his%20own%20orchestration%2C%20Modi%20has%20assiduously%20been%20built%20up%20as%20a%20cult%20personality%2C%20and%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20context%20even%20been%20conferred%20the%20status%20of%20a%20semi-deity%20by%20acolytes.%20His%20image%20as%20a%20dominant%20figure%20guiding%20the%20child-Ram%20to%20his%20half-built%20abode%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20flooding%20social%20media%20and%20the%20airwaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20catch%3A%20Throughout%20the%20regions%20where%20the%20BJP%20matters%20in%20substantial%20measure%2C%20the%20sustained%20BJP-RSS%20propaganda%2C%20the%20communal%20cultural%20penetration%20and%20the%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20saffron%20party%20in%20the%20last%20election%20have%20already%20reached%20a%20saturation%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20there%20seems%20little%20scope%20for%20the%20propaganda%20and%20the%20hype%20associated%20with%20the%20January%2022%20inauguration%20in%20Ayodhya%20yielding%20significantly%20more%20parliament%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-rss-bjp-vhp-ram-temple%5C%22%3EFour%20Decades%20of%20Milking%20a%20Deity%20in%20Ayodhya%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-parties-after-the-defeat-preparing-for-2024%5C%22%3EINDIA%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20differences%20within%20parties%20on%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20to%20contest%20are%20real%2C%20but%20these%20are%20chiefly%20limited%20to%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20possibly%20Punjab%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20are%20unlikely%20to%20impact%20the%20consolidated%20kitty%20of%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20in%20terms%20of%20seats%20won.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20smoothing%20over%20of%20difficulties%20will%20have%20a%20positive%20national%20effect%20in%20projecting%20to%20the%20electorate%20a%20combination%20with%20a%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20differences%20in%20the%20BJP%20camp%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20appear%20more%20searing.%20Open%20evidence%20of%20this%20is%20the%20apparent%20resentment%20of%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20CM%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20at%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20was%20eased%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20mood%20is%20said%20to%20be%20sullen%20among%20the%20most%20important%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20too.%20They%20had%20been%20pushed%20aside%20by%20Modi%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20polls.%20In%20UP%2C%20the%20unhappiness%20of%20the%20key%20players%20of%20the%20state%20government%20with%20the%20presiding%20duo%20at%20the%20Centre%20is%20no%20secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20EVM%20factor%2C%20widely%20thought%20to%20be%20weighted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20establishment%3B%20the%20vast%20money%20resources%20in%20the%20grasp%20of%20the%20Modi%20BJP%3B%20and%20the%20wind%20that%20the%20mainstream%20media%20puts%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20sails%20distinctly%20discomfit%20the%20opposition.%20But%20the%20pre-election%20political%20landscape%20is%20not%20any%20more%20a%20one-way%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanand-k-sahay%5C%22%3EAnand%20K.%20Sahay%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20political%20commentator%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20in%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705578886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpolitical-landscape-no-longer-one-sided%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20anything%2C%20differences%20within%20the%20BJP%20camp%20appear%20more%20searing%20than%20differences%20on%20seat-sharing%20within%20the%20INDIA%20coalition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpolitical-landscape-no-longer-one-sided%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raducanu%20out%20of%20Australian%20Open%20after%20strugglin